          <li>Modern employee lounge and break room facilities</li>
          <li>Professional finishes appropriate for public sector environment</li>
          <li>Coordination with government procurement and oversight requirements</li>
          <li>On-time delivery maintaining budget accountability</li>
        </ul>

        <p>The State Board of Education project reflects Northway Construction's commitment to serving Utah's educational and public sector institutions with professionalism, quality, and respect for taxpayer investment.</p>
